{"tid":1565334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★自由黨建議特首全民派發一萬元舒氣","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T07:59:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"dab2b39a0542f37f454a82b2642f44e10ecce9b8","tid":1565334,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"13.09.2019 13:50<br />\n自由黨早上與行政長官林鄭月娥見面，反映對新一份《施政報告》的意見，建議全民派發一萬元，讓市民「舒舒氣」，並建議特區政府與深圳政府商討，利用落馬洲河套區用作興建港深創新科技園的土地，改建公營房屋。被問到河套區土地的擁有權屬於深圳，自由黨主席張宇人表示，不清楚兩地政府的協議細則，自由黨只是拋出概念，期望加快土地供應進度。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨並建議向零售、飲食業等商戶，每間提供一萬元資助額，又表示因應部分廠商移師海外，建議在海外設立香港工業園。被問到自由黨會否支持引用《收回土地條例》建屋，黨魁鍾國斌認為公私營合作發展土地較好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1170697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1170697&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=c912b391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1170697</a>"},{"pid":"a76901cad14124e54c462758eaf654d8cc2bb7ab","tid":1565334,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a29168f7c65df917feed1cf91db900773cccf7f","tid":1565334,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"dcfac22ef24563add412b25c5cef9bdcfe39077f","tid":1565334,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f2cbfc62ac27e573735897d9060c02924297a9","tid":1565334,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a76901cad14124e54c462758eaf654d8cc2bb7ab","tid":1565334,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一皮已經收買唔到人心"},{"pid":"8d67de691368eff7a783a9619bbde9470507b3ff","tid":1565334,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:07:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"065d9444888f55dbf2815d88c72c9f226d07